    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready to hit the road! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition, showing some signs of its journeys but still offering a solid and functional driving experience. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a practical, budget-friendly option that gets the job done with a positive spirit!",
